          "description": "Maya Rubin is an outstanding professional who listens carefully and gives very experienced advice. Always willing to discuss and explain different ways of deciding on medical issues and treatment. The office is of the highest quality with no detail overlooked to create a pleasant environment. Support team is also efficient and pleasant to deal with. One Medical should serve as a model for better health care delivery.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WTmFGTmhabGMyUTB4clYycG1SeTFTVm01RU0zYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x252ee794eae03cc6!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOnVNaFNhZlc2Q0xrV2pmRy1SVm5EM3c%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "Edited a month ago",
