          "date_iso8601": "2026-02-10T12:41:05+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Xiao Wei",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "102601758902058358051",
          "user_review_count": 10,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4nsbecKl_0Df0iJuCe6XS96aJKXXuYXCv9FyA6FcPUaAL6PQHZw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Too corporate now. If you\u2019re 15 min late to your free annual physical, they will convert it to a problem based visit and charge you a $45 copay.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21FMGVrMVBTVFJPVmtkR1luYzFSelZXVHpFemRFRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x252ee794eae03cc6!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmE0ek1PSTROVkdGYnc1RzVWTzEzdEE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "3 weeks ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-06-04T12:55:42+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "J",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "116904195748200720111",
          "user_review_count": 99,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUk8adDWvpE-Dqp2SAQx_mcUUVPZRqqSckCVFMuV94xdR6-A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "There's a nurse practitioner here (or who was here) who probably saved my life: Lorraine Jaysura. Some doctors rush and have no bedside manner, but despite OM's policy of clipping appointments along so that people aren't kept waiting long (which is nice) she still found a way to make you feel heard which in turn allowed her to set up adequate care and referrals. She upholds medical ethics and human empathy all in one person, and her insight and action helped to quickly start rectifying issues that had plagued me for far too long. I will try and find a way to thank her directly too but wanted to leave this for anyone else searching for quality concierge care.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VQVGVuS3l4NTgyclRREAE!2m1!1s0x0:0x252ee794eae03cc6!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEPTenKyx582rTQ%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "a year ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2025-06-04T13:43:02+00:00"
        },
