          "description": "The One Medical in NoMad is one of...if not THE BEST medical offices I have had the pleasure to work with regarding my health. Dr. \"Kash\"...much appreciation for keeping an optimistic smile/face I discussing major changes and challenges regarding my health and overall communication!",
