          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVcuuhwKXdhJqB962qnWv31rC8ihm3n5Ze22M9AGWVux_VnJCti=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Excellent interpersonal skills, warm, open, inviting, communicative, responsive and respectful.  I feel like a unique human being when I am there and treated as a peer.  I am also held accountable to what my doctor believes is important to maintaining my good health.  Excellent record keeping to give me a history of my medical needs and care.  Excellent maintenance of communication with my other medical institutions.",
